Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. In small bowl, whisk together butter, pepper sauce and vinegar. Dip drumettes in butter mixture; arrange in single layer in large baking pan. Sprinkle with Hidden Valley(R) Original Ranch(R) Salad Dressing & Seasoning Mix. Bake until chicken is browned and an internal temperature of 165 degrees F has been reached, about 30 to 40 minutes. Sprinkle with paprika. Serve with Hidden Valley(R) Original Ranch(R) Dressing and celery sticks.